{"TopicId":76911,"ForumId":39,"TopicTitle":"I Made Kerbin","CreatedByName":"Thomas988","CreatedById":92699,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-07-07T20:14:48Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Thomas988","CreatedById":92699,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-07-07T20:14:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EOk, I think it\u0027s safe to say Gimp is one of the best softwares ever. I watched a tutorial on how to make planets, and I decided to use that knowledge to make Kerbin. I\u0027m impressed with what I made. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/dbLiS3G.png\u0022 alt=\u0022dbLiS3G.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheShadow1138","CreatedById":53694,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-07-07T21:29:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EIt is indeed most impressive. Well done sir.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Fleet Master","CreatedById":78352,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-07-07T21:30:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ECan someone say new picture for my slideshow Backround? It\u0027s beautiful.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Whirligig Girl","CreatedById":36077,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-07-08T16:59:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EYou made Kerbin? Kerbin\u0027s mother has some stretch marks that disagree with you. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Thomas988","CreatedById":92699,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-07-08T19:14:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022GregroxMun\u0022 data-cite=\u0022GregroxMun\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EYou made Kerbin? Kerbin\u0027s mother has some stretch marks that disagree with you. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EOk, that made me lol. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Thomas988","CreatedById":92699,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-07-09T12:16:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EOMG! This was featured on the KSP Facebook page! \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"_Augustus_","CreatedById":115084,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-12-27T19:52:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EHow do you do that? \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_huh.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:confused:\u0022\u003E sorry for necro\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Thomas988","CreatedById":92699,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-12-27T20:23:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EIt\u0027s quite complicated, I\u0027m afraid. First I got a map of Kerbin (2048 by 1024 pixels I believe), and a cloud map at the same resolution. Then, in Gimp, I made the Kerbin map one layer and the clouds another. I then merged the layers together and went to Filters\u0026gt;Map\u0026gt;Map Object and messed with the settings until it made a sphere. Now, I could continue for another paragraph on what I did to get the final product, but that would be too long and complicated. So, I\u0027ll link the video I watched on how to do this. It isn\u0027t a tutorial, so if you\u0027re like me you\u0027ll have to watch it over a couple times to understand what\u0027s going on. But, it is all there, and it is the exact same technique I used.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EEDIT: Here\u0027s where I got the map of Kerbin from. \u003Ca href=\u0022http://www.kerbalmaps.com/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://www.kerbalmaps.com/\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Ciframe src=\u0022https://player.vimeo.com/video/39974514\u0022 width=\u0022640\u0022 height=\u0022480\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 title=\u0022Creating a planet in The GIMP\u0022 allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rjtaml","CreatedById":111319,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-12-27T20:27:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EYou sir, deserve, a rep.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"CG_Kerbin","CreatedById":117777,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-12-27T20:56:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EHow have I not seen this it\u0027s great\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MartGonzo","CreatedById":65764,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-12-27T21:12:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ETruly stunning \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Thomas988","CreatedById":92699,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-12-27T23:06:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EWow, geez guys! Thanks for the support! \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E Maybe I\u0027ll redo Kerbin, or make another planet, who knows.\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}